  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil and cook the spaghetti according to the package instructions until al dente.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the peruvian olive oil over medium heat and add the diced red onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the diced peruvian aji amarillo pepper and cook for an additional 2 minutes until tender.",
    "Add the rendered lardons to the skillet and cook until crispy.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cooked spaghetti, crispy lardons, and pepper mixture.",
    "Top the spaghetti with shaved grana padano cheese and chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
